cdata.name: Paygine
cdata.desc:
Paygineis a cryptocurrencyfinancial platform based on Best2Pay company processing center. Using an automaticcrypto-to-fiatconversion system, itprovides the users (businesses and customers) with the tools to deal with cryptocurrencyas their ordinary currency. Payginefeatures the possibility to maintain wallets in both fiat and cryptocurrencies, and convert funds between them as well as to transact cryptocurrency to and from a bank card.

The PGC token is an Ethereum-based (ERC20) cryptocurrency. It will act as the basic functional tool to the Paygineusers, allowing them to have 10% to 30% discount when using the PGC token to pay for goods and services.
